For Debian Squeeze

THIS SCRIPT IS MEANT TO BE RUN ON A NEW OR JUST REINS TALLED SERVER
Some programs such as Apache & Samba are removed by this script.

The file setup-debian.sh has to be on your server.
For the initial setup git may not be installed on your server.
If wget is installed try
wget https://github.com/Keith2/lowendscript-ng/blob/master/setup-debian.sh

For intitial server setup run
bash setup-debian.sh all

To install Friendica for domain example.com, after the initial server setup run
bash setup-debian.sh friendica example.com





